value.readme:
Frequently-used unicode for quantum notation


https://github.com/j6k4m8/espanso-quantum

| Abbreviation | Expansion |
|--------------|-----------|
|<kbd>\\\\to</kbd> | → |
|<kbd>\\\\bn</kbd> | ℕ |
|<kbd>\\\\br</kbd> | ℝ |
|<kbd>\\\\pi</kbd> | π |
|<kbd>\\\\bb</kbd> | 𝔹 |
|<kbd>\\\\cdot</kbd> | ⋅ |
|<kbd>\\\\theta</kbd> | θ |
|<kbd>\\\\psi</kbd> | ψ |
|<kbd>\\\\lambda</kbd> | λ |
|<kbd>\\\\neg</kbd> | ¬ |
|<kbd>\\\\times</kbd> | × |
|<kbd>\\\\pm</kbd> | ± |
|<kbd>\\\\b1</kbd> | 𝟙 |
|<kbd>\\\\bra</kbd> | ⟨ |
|<kbd>\\\\ket</kbd> | ⟩ |

packageYml.name: package.yml
packageYml.content:
matches:
  - trigger: "\\\\to"
    replace: "→"
  - trigger: "\\\\bbN"
    replace: "ℕ"
  - trigger: "\\\\bbR"
    replace: "ℝ"
  - trigger: "\\\\pi"
    replace: "π"
  - trigger: "\\\\bbB"
    replace: "𝔹"
  - trigger: "\\\\cdot"
    replace: "⋅"
  - trigger: "\\\\theta"
    replace: "θ"
  - trigger: "\\\\psi"
    replace: "ψ"
  - trigger: "\\\\lambda"
    replace: "λ"
  - trigger: "\\\\neg"
    replace: "¬"
  - trigger: "\\\\times"
    replace: "×"
  - trigger: "\\\\pm"
    replace: "±"
  - trigger: "\\\\bb1"
    replace: "𝟙"
  - trigger: "\\\\bra"
    replace: "⟨"
  - trigger: "\\\\ket"
    replace: "⟩"
